    Adobe firefly

    Adobe Firefly is a new web application that harnesses the power of generative AI to enhance creativity. With Firefly, anyone can use simple text prompts to quickly generatehighest-quality output — beautiful images, text effects, and fresh color palettes. We can also make all-new content from reference images and explore more possibilities, more quickly.Note that these prompts can be used with Midjourney, LeonardoAI, DALL-E or any other image to text generation apps.

    Major features from Adobe firefly include:

    1. Text to Image: Generate images from a detailed text description.
    2. Generative Fill: Use a brush to remove objects or paint in new ones.
    3. Text Effects: Apply styles or textures to words and phrases.
    4. Generative Recolor: Generate color variations of your vector artwork.
    5. 3D to Image: Generate images from the interactive positioning of 3D elements.
    6. Project Stardust: Move any object anywhere in your image.

    In this guide we will focus on 250+ prompts that you can use to generate creative images from text to image feature. Feel free to playaround with new words for creative images.

    As Firefly evolves, Adobe aims to give creators more ability to train models on their own content and is engaging with the community around developments. Adobe’s approach is grounded in ethical AI principles like accountability, responsibility, and transparency.
